ygData.subject: Valen Nostrolo
ygData.msgSnippet: What level do you think you need to bo to complete this quest. I think I might know how to complete the quest, but I haven t been around there lately. He said
ygData.messageBody:
What level do you think you need to bo to complete this quest. I think
I might know how to complete the quest, but I haven't been around there
lately. He said that a hermit stole his pages, right? I saw a hermit in
a house in South Karanas, but the door was locked. I thought maybe if I
could get someone to open it for me, I could finish the quest.

Just a thought. I may try it this weekend, and see what happend. I most
certainly am not ready for it, if the reqard is a level 30 song, I am
just about level 10.

Oh, by the way, I ahve been making the Freeport to Qeynos trip
frequently since level 7. I made the trip from Qeynos to South Karana
at level 6, I think. Travelling is fun. Don't underestimate the gift of
sheer speed.


Mandibal
Cazic-Thule

Just a thought...
